
 google-apps-openid
 ==================
 
 This site hosts OpenID discovery information in XRDS necessary for Google Apps Hosted Dommains OpenID to work.

 To use your Hosted Dommains account as OpenID, enter http://your.hostname/openid as the login URL.

 You will get an OpenID identifier like http://your.hostname/openid?id=<number>


 The original Google documentation can be found here:

 http://groups.google.com/group/google-federated-login-api/web/openid-discovery-for-hosted-domains


